The use of neural networks also suggests that the paper could fall under machine learning (cs.MM) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the detection of specific regions in an image, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper's potential applications in image compression and restoration could also place it under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
